title: Slayer/Level up table
content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Slayer/Level up table
LevelNew abilities

  • You must talk to Turael to start Slayer before you are able to use other Slayer masters. Alternatively, the Natural history quiz miniquest can be completed to level up to 9 and then use any Slayer master available to the player.
